description: Introduction to non-linear dynamics, chaos, bifurcation, and qualitative analysis of continuous and discrete dynamical systems and their use in understanding complex behavior of systems. Emphasis will be placed on understanding qualitative features of models of electrical, mechanical, and biological systems.
name: CHAOT DYNAM ELEC & BIOL: Dynamics and Bifurcations in Engineering Systems
